<body>

  <div class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <a href="../index.html" class="back-link"><i class="bi bi-arrow-left me-1"></i> Back to Portfolio</a>
      <h1>Storyboard <span>2</span></h1>
      <p>PrestigeCuts Barbershop · Light Theme · SEG3125 Assignment 2 · Majd Al Khori — 300240467</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container">

    <!-- Persona -->
    <div class="persona-card">
      <div class="row align-items-start">
        <div class="col-lg-7">
          <h3>Persona: <span>Robert</span></h3>
          <div class="role">Accountant, 54 — Ottawa</div>
          <div>
            <span class="persona-tag">Not very tech-savvy</span>
            <span class="persona-tag">Prefers calling ahead</span>
            <span class="persona-tag">Values clear information</span>
            <span class="persona-tag">Long-time barbershop client</span>
          </div>
          <div class="persona-goal">
            <strong style="color:#1a6b3a;">Goal:</strong> Robert wants to find out where the barbershop is located, what the opening hours are, and how much a basic haircut costs — so he can decide whether to stop by after work on Friday.
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4 offset-lg-1 mt-4 mt-lg-0">
          <p style="font-size:0.82rem; color:#999; margin-bottom:6px;">Relation to technology</p>
          <p style="font-size:0.85rem; color:#555; margin-bottom:16px;">Uses his phone mostly for calls and email. He can browse websites but gets frustrated if things are hard to find or too cluttered. Prefers simple, clear layouts.</p>
          <p style="font-size:0.82rem; color:#999; margin-bottom:6px;">Relation to barbershops</p>
          <p style="font-size:0.85rem; color:#555; margin:0;">Has been going to barbershops his whole life. Not interested in booking apps — he'd rather call. But he'll look up a new place online before committing.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Steps -->
    <div class="row g-4 align-items-start">

      <!-- Step 1 -->
      <div class="col-lg-4">
        <div class="step-label">Step</div>
        <div class="step-num">01</div>
        <div class="step-title">Robert finds the site</div>
        <div class="step-desc">He Googles "barbershop Ottawa Sparks Street" and lands on the homepage. He scrolls slowly, reading everything.</div>

        <div class="mockup-frame">
          <div class="mockup-bar">
            <div class="mockup-dot" style="background:#ff5f57;"></div>
            <div class="mockup-dot" style="background:#febc2e;"></div>
            <div class="mockup-dot" style="background:#28c840;"></div>
            <span class="mockup-url">prestigecuts.ca</span>
          </div>
          <div class="m-nav">
            <div class="m-nav-brand">Prestige<span>cuts</span></div>
            <div class="m-nav-links">
              <a href="#">Services</a>
              <a href="#">Book</a>
              <a href="#">Contact</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="m-hero">
            <div class="m-hero-label">Ottawa's Local Barbershop</div>
            <h2>Look Good,<br /><em>Feel Better.</em></h2>
            <p>Small barbershop on Sparks Street. Good cuts, fair prices. Walk in or book ahead.</p>
            <span class="m-btn-green">Book a Cut</span>
          </div>
          <div class="m-services" style="padding:8px 14px;">
            <div style="font-size:0.6rem; color:#bbb;">↓ Scrolling down...</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-lg-4 d-none d-lg-flex align-items-center justify-content-center" style="padding-top:160px;">
        <i class="bi bi-arrow-right" style="font-size:1.8rem; color:#1a6b3a;"></i>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2 -->
      <div class="col-lg-4">
        <div class="step-label">Step</div>
        <div class="step-num">02</div>
        <div class="step-title">He checks the services and prices</div>
        <div class="step-desc">He scrolls to the services section. He sees the Classic Haircut is $35. That's reasonable to him — he makes a note.</div>

        <div class="mockup-frame">
          <div class="mockup-bar">
            <div class="mockup-dot" style="background:#ff5f57;"></div>
            <div class="mockup-dot" style="background:#febc2e;"></div>
            <div class="mockup-dot" style="background:#28c840;"></div>
            <span class="mockup-url">prestigecuts.ca/#services</span>
          </div>
          <div class="m-nav">
            <div class="m-nav-brand">Prestige<span>cuts</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="m-services">
            <div class="m-services-title">Our Services</div>
            <div class="m-service-row">
              <div class="m-service-item">
                <div class="name">Classic Haircut</div>
                <div class="price">$35</div>
              </div>
              <div class="m-service-item">
                <div class="name">Fade & Taper</div>
                <div class="price">$40</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="m-service-row">
              <div class="m-service-item">
                <div class="name">Beard Trim</div>
                <div class="price">$25</div>
              </div>
              <div class="m-service-item">
                <div class="name">Cut + Beard</div>
                <div class="price">$55</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div style="background:#f5f0e8; padding:8px 14px;">
            <div style="font-size:0.6rem; color:#bbb;">↓ Scrolling to contact...</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Step 3 -->
    <div class="row g-4 mt-2">
      <div class="col-12 text-center mb-2">
        <i class="bi bi-arrow-down" style="font-size:1.5rem; color:#1a6b3a;"></i>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-4 offset-lg-4">
        <div class="step-label">Step</div>
        <div class="step-num">03</div>
        <div class="step-title">He finds the address and hours</div>
        <div class="step-desc">He scrolls to the Contact section and finds everything he needed — address, phone number, and that they're open until 7pm on Fridays. He decides to walk in after work.</div>

        <div class="mockup-frame">
          <div class="mockup-bar">
            <div class="mockup-dot" style="background:#ff5f57;"></div>
            <div class="mockup-dot" style="background:#febc2e;"></div>
            <div class="mockup-dot" style="background:#28c840;"></div>
            <span class="mockup-url">prestigecuts.ca/#contact</span>
          </div>
          <div class="m-nav">
            <div class="m-nav-brand">Prestige<span>cuts</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="m-contact">
            <div class="m-contact-title">Find Us</div>
            <div class="m-contact-item">
              <i class="bi bi-geo-alt-fill"></i>
              <div>
                <div class="lbl">Address</div>
                <div class="info">145 Sparks Street, Ottawa, ON</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="m-contact-item">
              <i class="bi bi-telephone-fill"></i>
              <div>
                <div class="lbl">Phone</div>
                <div class="info">(613) 555-0192</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="m-hours">
            <table>
              <tr><td>Mon – Fri</td><td>9:00 AM – 7:00 PM</td></tr>
              <tr><td>Saturday</td><td>9:00 AM – 5:00 PM</td></tr>
              <tr><td>Sunday</td><td style="color:#dc3545 !important;">Closed</td></tr>
            </table>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Nav to other storyboard -->
    <div class="mt-5 pt-3" style="border-top: 1px solid #ddd;">
      <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center flex-wrap gap-3">
        <div>
          <p style="font-size:0.75rem; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.1em; color:#bbb; margin-bottom:4px;">Also see</p>
          <a href="storyboard1.html" style="color:#1a1a1a; font-weight:600; font-size:0.95rem;"><i class="bi bi-arrow-left me-1"></i> Storyboard 1 — Karim (Dark Theme)</a>
        </div>
        <a href="https://prestigecuts-barbershop.netlify.app" target="_blank" style="color:#1a6b3a; font-size:0.88rem;">View Live Site <i class="bi bi-box-arrow-up-right ms-1"></i></a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="page-footer">
    <span>SEG3125 Assignment 2 · Majd Al Khori · 300240467 · University of Ottawa</span><br />
    <a href="../index.html">Portfolio</a>
